{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ At the start of your opponent's turn, add one of your shields to your hand. Then add the top 2 cards of your deck to your shields face down. (You may use the "shield trigger" ability of the shield added to your hand this way.)
■ Labyrinth: If you have more shields than your opponent, each of your Metallica gets +5000 power.

{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ You may untap this creature to change your opponent's creatures attack to this creature or one of your tapped creatures.
■ Labyrinth: Whenever your opponent would choose a creature, if you have more shields than your opponent, they can't choose your other Metallicas. (They can still be attacked or blocked.)

{NEO EVOLUTION}: You may put it on one of your Light creatures. (If a creature is under it, treat it as a Neo Evolution Creature.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, choose up to 2 of your opponent's creatures and tap them. If this is a Neo Evolution Creature, the chosen creatures don't untap at the start of your opponent's next turn.
